---

<section class="container py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="grid gap-16 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
    <!-- Image -->
    <div class="relative aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden rounded-sm bg-stone-100">
      <img
        src="/images/founder.jpg"
        alt="Pam Sweeney, founder of Purest Electrolyte"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground">Founder</p>
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl tracking-tight md:text-4xl">
        I started Purest because I couldn't find anything I trusted.
      </h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-foreground/80">
        <p>
          I was standing in the supplement aisle reading label after label. Everything
          claimed to be "clean." Nothing was. Artificial flavors, mystery sweeteners,
          dyes that had no business being in a hydration product.
        </p>
        <p>
          So I went home and made my own. Freeze-dried real fruit. Celtic sea salt.
          Nothing else. I made it for myself first — then my family. Then I couldn't
          stop giving it to everyone I knew.
        </p>
        <p>
          Purest exists because I believe you deserve to know exactly what you're
          putting in your body. No fine print. No hiding. Just the truth, visible
          in every jar.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="font-serif text-lg italic text-foreground/60">— Pam Sweeney, Founder</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
